race.comment: LAKEVIEW LIAM (4) was a last start winner (24.54) at Sale who is building a strong winning record. Has a strong winning record here. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Form reads well for this. SAXON KELTON (1) did a good job to finish second last time out over 400m at this track (22.79) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Expected to do much better this time. FEIKUAI CALVIN (5) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from three starts. In the money last time at Sale (24.67) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4.5 lengths second. Looks suited here and can measure up. ENZOLA (7) must be included in calculations.
